msgid "Change the author of the current gallery"
msgstr "Изменить автора текущей галереи"

#: ../admin/partials/actions/gallery-photo-gallery-admin-actions.php:1719
msgid ""
"You can change the author who created the current gallery to your preferred "
"one. You need to write the User ID here. Please note, that in case you write "
"an ID, by which there are no users found, the changes will not be applied "
"and the previous author will remain the same."
